 19	 * other half. These converters collapse a decoded page to this locale's plain
 20	 * strings + a `RichTextRun[]` the renderer maps to DOM — exactly the role
 21	 * `toConference` plays for the Conference boundary (`boundary-discipline`).
 22	 *
 23	 * Why a dedicated module rather than methods on `Content`: keeping the service
 24	 * interface small (`getPage` only) and the heterogeneous per-page projection in
 25	 * one boundary module honors `small-interface-deep-implementation`. A route does
 26	 * `toAboutView(yield* content.getPage('about'), locale)`; React sees only the
 27	 * view type, never a bilingual `Text` or a branded `href` (`derive-dont-sync`:
